s":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31 5p Progress Report — AHV DTLX/QLHV] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV DTLX (Đào Tạo Lái Xe) ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, task started/completed, blocker appeared), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis-DTLX — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 3:38 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 15:38 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776181164726,"__openclaw":{"id":"ecb5b6c5","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions_list and the heartbeat state from memory to detect any changes."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3cuqteojojb1_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3cuqteojojb1_2","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"heartbeat state sessions DTLX 5p report","maxResults":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":430,"output":96,"totalTokens":14470,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776181164902,"responseId":"062d92ae7a8ea965d5e879