nd `cron:ed2d0b5d`—but the second one appears twice because I was listing the cron job itself alongside its child sessions. So the baseline and current state are actually identical; nothing has changed, so I should stay silent."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current state (15:34 UTC) against baseline (15:27 UTC):\n\n**Baseline (15:27 UTC):** `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ `cron:e7885813` ✅ `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ — all running.\n\n**Current (15:34 UTC):** Same 4 sessions all still running. No new failures, no new blockers, no state transitions.\n\n**No change — silent exit.**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":30237,"output":515,"totalTokens":45104,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":408,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776181109603,"responseId":"062d9276ff174e8fce757c958e80d109","__openclaw":{"id":"4614a4c1","seq":5}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776180677753,"sessionId":"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":151387,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776162044660,"endedAt":1776162158012,"runtimeMs":113352,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun"